  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Cold Weather Payment estimates: 2018 to 2019
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Estimated number of eligible recipients, and triggers for Cold Weather Payments made in Great Britain from 1 November 2018 to 29 March 2019.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

