<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<div class="call-to-action">
<p>Find out about getting a <a href="https://www.gov.uk/cold-weather-payment">Cold Weather Payment</a>.</p>
</div>

<p>The Social Fund Cold Weather Payments scheme runs from 1 November 2018 to 31 March 2019. This is known as the Cold Weather Payment season.</p>

<p>The estimated number of eligible recipients and triggers in the data tables are to 29 March 2019.</p>

<p>Next release: 10 April 2019 – with data from 1 November 2018 to 31 March 2019.</p>

</div>
</div>

